title: Tooltip System Test
text:
This document demonstrates the tooltip system with various examples.


Display Text Override: - {{spell:133 â€œFBâ€}} (custom display text) - {{custom.items:free_action_potion â€œFAPâ€}} (abbreviated name)
Flag Testing: - [Fireball] (no inline icon) - {{spell:2136 â€œFire Blastâ€ no-icon}} (custom text, no icon) - [Free Action Potion] (has inline icon but no tooltip icon) - {{spell:116 â€œFrostboltâ€ no-icon no-tooltip-icon}} (minimal display)
ENCHANT: [Enchant Weapon - Crusader]
Mixed Examples: Use {{spell:133 â€œFBâ€}} and {{spell:2136 â€œFB2â€ no-icon}} in your rotation for maximum DPS.



Custom Curated Spells: - [Fireball] (curated content) - [Greater Heal] (curated healing spell)
Enchantment Spell: - [Enchant Weapon - Crusader] (enchanting profession spell with reagents)
Fallback to Database: Basic spell reference: [Fireball]
Spell with custom text: Use [Fireball] in your rotation.
Multiple spells: Mages should cast [Frostbolt] or [Fire Blast].



Free Action Potion: [Free Action Potion]
With abbreviation: Bring [Free Action Potion] to every BWL raid.
Multiple items: Stack up on [Greater Fire Protection Potion] and [Free Action Potion].
Crafted item with crafting info: [Dark Iron Bracers] (shows secondary crafting frame)
Legendary: Have you seen [Thunderfury, Blessed Blade of the Windseeker]?
Flask: Pop your [Flask of Supreme Power] before pull.



Achievement reference: [Naxxramas Conqueror]
With custom text: We [Naxxramas Conqueror] last month!
Another: Remember our [Onyxia's Lair]?



A typical raid preparation guide:

Bring [Free Action Potion] x20 for movement impairs
Bring [Greater Fire Protection Potion] x20 for fire damage
Flask users should use [Flask of Supreme Power]
Mages: Spec into [Blast Wave] for AoE trash
Warriors: Keep [Shield Block] up on bosses




Non-existent spell: [Missing entry] (should show â€œMissing entryâ€)
Non-existent custom item: [Missing entry] (should show â€œMissing entryâ€)



Notice how items display in different colors based on rarity:

[Free Action Potion] (common - white)
[Dark Iron Bracers] (uncommon - green)

[Flask of Supreme Power] (epic - purple)
[Thunderfury, Blessed Blade of the Windseeker] (legendary - orange)

And achievements in epic purple: [Naxxramas Conqueror]





Phase 1: - Tank positions boss at north wall - Melee stack behind boss - Ranged spread 10 yards apart - Use [Free Action Potion] when you get [Brood Affliction: Bronze]
Phase 2 (Breath Combos): - Fire + Shadow: Pop [Greater Fire Protection Potion] - Frost + Nature: Priests use [Power Word: Shield] on raid - Arcane + Time Lapse: Just heal through it
Consumables: - Main tank: [Flask of Supreme Power] + [Greater Fire Protection Potion] - Healers: Max mana consumables - DPS: [Flask of Supreme Power] if available
Achievement: Clear this for [Naxxramas Conqueror]!
